    "To better investigate the impact of long-term memory, we compare the proposed REFLECTOOL and other agent-based methods under different types of few-shot.",
    "As shown in Table 4, long-term memory can effectively improve the performance of all agent-based methods.",
    "However, the proposed methods, REFLECTOOL, still outperform all baselines with both types of few-shot samples.",
    "The results again show the effectiveness of the tool-wise reflection mechanism.",
    "To better investigate the impact of REFLECTOOL on tool selection, we visualize the tool distribution of different methods across various datasets in we exclude Trustworthiness in the visualization of the tool distribution."
